This paper is about language understanding tasks and benchmarks, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses pretraining and transfer learning methods, which are common in deep learning and could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of a software toolkit and public leaderboard, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
